          "prompt_html": "<h1>MULTIPLE CHOICE 01</h1><p><strong>Questions 15 - 20</strong></p><p>Choose <strong>two</strong> correct options, <strong>A - E</strong>.</p><p>Write them in any order in answer boxes.</p><p>Which TWO of the following are true of the Students' Union building?</p><p>15</p><p>16</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    You need to be a member to access its facilities.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    All eating and drinking facilities are located on the same floor.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    It is a good place to go if you want to find out about joining student groups or clubs.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>D</strong>    You can play football there.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>E</strong>    It always closes at the same time.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Which TWO of the following does the guide say about the library?</p><p>17</p><p>18</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    Students can get part-time work there.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    It is the main reason most students chose to come to the university.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    Students should visit it as soon as possible.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>D</strong>    Students can have tours of it throughout the year.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>E</strong>    It has different opening hours at certain times of the year.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Which TWO of the following are true of the university sports hall?</p><p>19</p><p>20</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    It is the newest building at the university.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    It is very popular.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    You need to pay extra to use it.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>D</strong>    You can get a map there.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>E</strong>    You can use your discount card there.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>",
